{"title":"筛地歌——写给黄河故道","authors":["陈咏华"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":9,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"筛地歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——写给黄河故道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈咏华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人说，昔日这里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吸一口气沙粒夹牙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走一步路砂石打架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茅草瘦成针尖尖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地瓜没有拳头大！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又有人说，昔日这里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枯黄的砂石血泪里泡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泡成遍地穷疙瘩！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砂石水呀染黄了穷人的牙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砂礓石呀就象大地的疤……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十年前红旗来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里淮北放光彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵黄河、鞭故道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻天覆地好气概！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声“筛地”喊出口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拳头捏出声音来——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“看咱把地层分个细，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荒山的帽子筛中甩！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一铲铲添，一筛筛分，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千筛转一转，荒山都变矮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干部带了头，社员汗不揩！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砂石七分一旁滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细土三分造田来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地球转一圈，筛盘万回摆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝霞筛中飞，星光筛中白……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筛了头年新苗栽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筛了二年金银来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筛走数九彻骨寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水流得更畅快！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更喜十月春雷响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万象更新除四害。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政策落实东风起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千树万树红花开——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"令砂粒，将那大厦盖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教石子，筑路朝未来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤橙黄绿青蓝紫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓淡相宜巧安排！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筛出了稻棉，筛出了麦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筛得春色浓似海……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家说，现在这里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吸一口空气新鲜三年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走一步路看千幅画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处是粮棉瓜果吐芳香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处是青枝绿叶满地插，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰苦奋斗传家宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的政策又开了花！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}